data.description: VIEWS VIEWS VIEWS!!! Welcome to this stunning single-story home that blends comfort and style in every corner. This charming abode boasts 4 spacious bedrooms, perfect for a growing family or those seeking extra space for a home office or guest rooms. With 3 bathrooms, morning routines are a breeze! The home offers an impressive 2,555 square feet of living space, providing ample room for relaxation and entertainment. Prepare to be captivated by breathtaking views that will greet you every day, reminding you of the beauty that surrounds this remarkable property. Don't miss the opportunity to make this house a place you'll proudly call home!
